{
  "stem": "7157.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you could go to Czechoslovakia on a one-day pass.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, of course, we never came back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had some family in-- in Czechoslovakia, so we stayed with-- with that family, one of these cousins I mentioned way back early.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "His name is Isko Geminder.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And was in a-- he survived because he was in the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was an officer in the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "His wife somehow survived Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But she did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were already in a city called Morawska-Ostrawa in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So my mother took us there, and we stayed there while she went back and got some things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then they came over to Czechoslovakia the same way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we stayed with them a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we made plans to go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "See, we had to go to West Germany, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Wasn't any good to go to East Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So, to West Germany-- that's why we went through Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were able to-- to find a guide.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he took us from Czechoslovakia to West Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In fact, I remember the snow was so high that at one point we had to actually dig tunnels in the snow to go through-- through the border.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we managed it and got to West Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was early in the game.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We hadn't, of course, contacted them yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when we got to Germany, we went to a-- we somehow wound up in a little city called Regensburg.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there, there was an UNRRA camp, United Nations rehabilitation-type camp, which was set up-- I say 'United Nations,' but in reality, it was primarily US-run camp, for displaced people, for orphans, for-- primarily for children that had lost their parents.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And again, this wasn't Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
